{"tid":1887320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府批新公務員工會集會明顯違反抗疫指引","createTime":"2020-02-19T12:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T13:30:53.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"389ca1bcc6dbde086d37033d00f90aceaf5a4d31","tid":1887320,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:29:15.000Z","msg":"新公務員工會晚上在政總東翼前地外集會，不滿政府防疫措施，包括防疫物資供應及警隊獲發較多物資等，約300人參與。政府回應時指，在疫情嚴峻的情況下，組織呼籲公務員和市民聚集，做法完全不負責任，對公務員和市民的安全置之不顧，並明顯有違政府減少社交接觸的重要抗疫指引。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，局方早前回覆已明確表示，防護衣的分配是按工作人員崗位涉及的風險而訂定，亦已多番公開作出解釋，但新工會似乎漠視，反而以不滿特別上班安排和政府物資分配準則為藉口，發動示威集會，政府對這種企圖分化公務員隊伍、製造矛盾、打擊公務員士氣的行徑，深表遺憾及失望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265324&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1265324%26csid%3D261_341&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5KnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=e0a4b560\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265324&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"da8a09fd02868ac096318767c2a66196410ec6fb","tid":1887320,"uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"唔係有不反咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f6fa64ace19c692c64e780980aebcbbe38bec8","tid":1887320,"uid":60924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿一哥呢"},{"pid":"4e473112dbfd5119db84066fe5852e39d4a358be","tid":1887320,"uid":78470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"私人集會"},{"pid":"d8eeb5f65fe3ca3f46398d52b4d40d4b61d71124","tid":1887320,"uid":286897,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"